      <title>陷入困境的房地产公司阿德勒与贷方达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/german-real-estate-firm-adler-reaches-agreement-with-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的德国房地产公司阿德勒集团 (Adler Group SA) 已与一些债券持有人就再次调整其债务负担达成原则协议，因为这家陷入困境的德国房地产公司正努力出售房产并提高流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/german-real-estate-firm-adler-reaches-agreement-with-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:34:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
